creator: Biutix UG
descriptionHtml:
Biutix is an innovative social network in which everyone who loves fashion and creativity will feel at home! Regardless of whether you are a fashion guru, model, entrepreneur, tattoo collector, selfie specialist, make-up artist, It-Girl, bad hair day savior, design pioneer, fashion photographer: Biutix is made with passion for you!

As of today, you only need an app to make a great presentation with your creations or your business. In Biutix you are the creator! Create or share video stories, outfits, collections or experience other cool topics beyond fashion.


Biutix supports you in unlocking your creative potential!

Have you just moved your furniture or found out how to make your old sloppy sweater with a trendy belt a real eye-catcher?


•Show us who you are! Upload your own styles or design and make followers and future employers aware of you!

•There is space in your Biutix profile for your special professional experiences, passions and visions. Present your new ideas or your business!

•Create Video stories of your creations or beautiful experiences. Share the best with friends and family!

•Stage all those moments with filters of our designer tool!

•The last big vacation is a while ago and the beautiful pictures of the white sandy beach and turquoise blue sea are buried somewhere in your uploads? At Biutix you can bring your most beautiful events back into the spotlight with the featured pictures!

•At Biutix you are more than just a photo! Show us your individuality with templates for your personal profile!

•Your magic box. A big event is just around the corner? And you saw gorgeous earrings in a designer’s account, a celebrity dress in another user's showroom? Put it straight into your magical wedding box! Graduation party box! ...

•Stay up2date! Follow your role models, designers, artists and creative people and take the latest trends with you!

•Fashion is not yours now? But photography? Or architecture? Whatever your strength or passion, at Biutix you can participate in other interesting topics
descriptionShort: Biutix connecting people who loves fashion, beauty, creativity and much moore.
